---
title: Herbed Chicken with Roasted Asparagus plus Prosciutto-Topped Mashed Potatoes, Pan Sauce & Chives
description: This French-inspired meal starts by searing herb-crusted chicken in a hot pan, which then roasts in the oven alongside seasoned asparagus. Over the top is a buttery shallot pan sauce swirled with fig jam for a hit of savory-sweetness. A luxe topping of crisped prosciutto levels up lusciously creamy mashed potatoes for a bistro-style meal to remember.
